Body:
It will not be in their power to frustrate Allah's Plan;
				all they will do is to go further and further down in
				their spiritual state, deeper and deeper in their Hell.

The attainment and satisfaction of all hopes and desires;
				the reaching of the final goal of Bliss. Cf. xliv. 57,
				and n. 47 33.

Din=the giving to each person his precise and just due;
				this is implied in Judgment and Justice. All the
				inequalities of this Life are to be redressed.

For baraa, 'to bring into existence', and other words
				denoting Allah's creative energy, see n. 120 to ii. 117;
				n. 916 to vi. 94; and n. 923 to vi. 98.
